==Torres Strait Creole==
===Noun===
'''[[smol]] [[koknat]]'''

# an [[immature]] [[coconut]]
===Usage note===
''Smol koknat'' or ''[[gad]]'' (eastern dialect) is the third stage of coconut growth. It is preceded by ''[[musu koknat]]'' (western dialect) or ''[[giru]]'' (eastern dialect) and followed by ''[[kopespes]]''.
